    "rationale": "The overall credibility assessment is Accepted. Eleven of thirteen credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels. The Test conditions factor achieved Gradation 2 against a Gradation 3 requirement; this shortfall is considered acceptable given the standardized ASTM F1717 protocol and the medium model risk level. The Model inputs and Output comparison factors have been reviewed and confirmed adequate by the assessment team. The ensemble of three independent FEA environments corroborates the prediction, and all pre-defined quantitative acceptance criteria (E/uval < 1.96; <10% QoI difference) are satisfied across all three quantities of interest.",
